														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2492755">
									

<p>Actually, looking close at SCP-2085, the details line up <em>really</em> well. Intentional or not, this, <a href="/scp-1637">SCP-1637</a>, and the lore surrounding Prometheus Labs make it a very likely origin for both the girl's biotech and Wizard's more bootlegged loadout. The clinic where they met (where Wizard was getting an overhaul when the girls raided the place) is almost certainly one of the spinoffs from PL's collapse, for instance.</p>
<p>Depending on how old they are, they might even have been one of the last sort-of-successful things Prometheus Labs produced, the 4.0 or whatever number they were on at that point for the project.</p>

