			<div class="content" id="post-content-2486478">
									

<p>I feel like the PLA uses human wave tactics so often because they have enough people that they can. They really don't need to buy these fancy automatons, and frankly the money will probably get stolen along the way by corrupt officials.</p>
<p>Personally, I envision rich Northern European nations trying to counteract Russian Aggression or maybe Japan in fear of China, where these countries have plenty of money to throw around but shrinking populations, making conscription of soldiers from citizens more problematic.</p>

